"<span class=\"h2-fs\"><strong>ເບິ່ງແຍງຊັບພະຍາກອນຂອງທ່ານ </strong></span>"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "<span class=\"h2-fs\">Make your customers happy </span>🆘"
msgstr "<span class=\"h2-fs\">ເຮັດໃຫ້ລູກຄ້າຂອງທ່ານມີຄວາມສຸກ </span>🆘"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong><span class=\"h2-fs\">Accounting made easy 🧮</span></strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong><span class=\"h2-fs\">ການບັນຊີກາຍເປັນເລື່ອງງ່າຍ 🧮</span></strong>"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong><span class=\"h2-fs\">Create an attractive website 🌐</span></strong>"
msgstr "<strong><span class=\"h2-fs\">ສ້າງເວັບໄຊທີ່ໜ້າສົນໃຈ 🌐</span></strong>"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong><span class=\"h2-fs\">Fleet 🚚</span></strong>"
msgstr "<strong><span class=\"h2-fs\">ຍານພາຫະນະ 🚚</span></strong>"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong><span class=\"h2-fs\">Sell product sets 🔩</span></strong>"
msgstr "<strong><span class=\"h2-fs\">ຂາຍເປັນຊຸດຜະລິດຕະພັນ 🔩</span></strong>"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"A good work cannot be achieved without motivated and skilled employees, "
"reliable equipment nor suitable vehicles."
msgstr ""
"ວຽກງານທີ່ດີບໍ່ສາມາດສຳເລັດໄດ້ ຫາກປາສະຈາກພະນັກງານທີ່ມີແຮງຈູງໃຈ ແລະ ມີທັກສະ, ອຸປະກອນທີ່ເຊື່ອຖືໄດ້ ຫຼື ຍ"
"ານພາຫະນະທີ່ເໝາະສົມ."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"A link to reach the online quotation from where the customer can confirm and"
" sign it."
msgstr ""
"ລິ້ງເພື່ອເຂົ້າເຖິງໃບສະເໜີລາຄາອອນລາຍ ເພື່ອໃຫ້ລູກຄ້າສາມາດຢືນຢັນ ແລະ ເຊັນຊື່ໄດ້."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "Accurately track the project 🔍"
msgstr "ຕິດຕາມໂຄງການຢ່າງຖືກຕ້ອງ 🔍"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"All these components will give you an accurate overview on the project "
"profitability."
msgstr ""
"ອົງປະກອບທັງໝົດເຫຼົ່ານີ້ຈະຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານເຫັນພາບລວມທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງກ່ຽວກັບກຳໄລຂອງໂຄງການ."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Amazing employees deserve amazing equipment. Make the sure all your tools are fit and well by tracking their health in the\n"
"            <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Maintenance</font></strong> app."
msgstr ""
"ພະນັກງານທີ່ດີເລີດສົມຄວນໄດ້ຮັບອຸປະກອນທີ່ດີເລີດ. ໃຫ້ແນ່ໃຈວ່າເຄື່ອງມືທັງໝົດຂອງທ່ານພ້ອມໃຊ້ງານຢູ່ສະເໝີ ໂດຍການ"
"ຕິດຕາມສະພາບຂອງພວກມັນໃນແອັບ\n"
"            <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ການບຳລຸງຮັກສາ</font></"
"strong>."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Analytic Items ➡️ Track any cost using Analytic Items from the Accounting "
"App"
msgstr "ລາຍການວິເຄາະ ➡️ ຕິດຕາມຄ່າໃຊ້ຈ່າຍຕ່າງໆ ໂດຍໃຊ້ລາຍການວິເຄາະຈາກແອັບການບັນຊີ"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "Architect"
msgstr "ສະຖາປະນິກ"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"As the first invoicing step, create a down payment from the sales order. This will generate the first invoice in the\n"
"            <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Invoicing</font></strong> app. Then, schedule one or several \"Invoicing Schedule\" activities on the sales order with the aim to never forget to send an intermediary invoice in order to sustain\n"
"            your cash flow."
msgstr ""
"ໃນຂັ້ນຕອນທຳອິດຂອງການອອກໃບເກັບເງິນ, ໃຫ້ສ້າງເງິນມັດຈຳຈາກໃບສັ່ງຂາຍ. ສິ່ງນີ້ຈະສ້າງໃບເກັບເງິນໃບທຳອິດໃ"
"ນແອັບ\n"
"            <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ການອອກໃບເກັບເງິນ</font></"
"strong>. ຈາກນັ້ນ, ກຳນົດກິດຈະກຳ \"ຕາຕະລາງການອອກໃບເກັບເງິນ\" ໜຶ່ງ ຫຼື ຫຼາຍລາຍການໃນໃບສັ່ງຂາຍ "
"ເພື່ອບໍ່ໃຫ້ພາດການສົ່ງໃບເກັບເງິນລະຫວ່າງການດຳເນີນງານ ເພື່ອຮັກສາ\n"
"            ກະແສເງິນສົດຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Assign the tasks to the right responsible and easily check the progress in "
"the Kanban view."
msgstr ""
"ມອບໝາຍໜ້າວຽກໃຫ້ຜູ້ຮັບຜິດຊອບທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ ແລະ ກວດສອບຄວາມຄືບໜ້າໄດ້ງ່າຍໆ ໃນມຸມມອງ Kanban."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"At any time, you can create from an opportunity a beautiful and tailor-made "
"quotation that displays the price, the discount, the unit of measure, and "
"the tax of each:"
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດສ້າງໃບສະເໜີລາຄາທີ່ສວຍງາມ ແລະ ປັບແຕ່ງໄດ້ຕາມຕ້ອງການຈາກໂອກາດການຂາຍ ເຊິ່ງຈະສະແດງລາຄ"
"າ, ສ່ວນຫຼຸດ, ຫົວໜ່ວຍວັດແທກ ແລະ ພາສີຂອງແຕ່ລະລາຍການ:"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "Basics"
msgstr "ພື້ນຖານ"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Before generating an intermediary invoice in the\n"
"            <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Invoicing</font></strong> app, freeze the project status in the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Project</font></strong> app to get an overview on the progress in terms of:"
msgstr ""
"ກ່ອນທີ່ຈະສ້າງໃບເກັບເງິນລະຫວ່າງການດຳເນີນງານໃນແອັບ\n"
"            <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ການອອກໃບເກັບເງິນ</font></"
"strong>, ໃຫ້ບັນທຶກສະຖານະຂອງໂຄງການໃນແອັບ <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ໂຄ"
"ງການ</font></strong> ເພື່ອເບິ່ງພາບລວມຂອງຄວາມຄືບໜ້າໃນດ້ານ:"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Before starting the project, make sure you have enough stock. The confirmation of the quotation also triggers the creation of a delivery in the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Inventory</font></strong>\n"
"            app where you can check the stock levels of each needed storable product."
msgstr ""
"ກ່ອນເລີ່ມໂຄງການ, ໃຫ້ແນ່ໃຈວ່າທ່ານມີສິນຄ້າໃນສາງພຽງພໍ. ການຢືນຢັນໃບສະເໜີລາຄາຍັງຈະກະຕຸ້ນໃຫ້ມີການສ້າງກາ"
"ນຈັດສົ່ງໃນແອັບ\n"
"            <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ສາງສິນຄ້າ</font></strong> ເຊິ່"
"ງທ່ານສາມາດກວດສອບລະດັບສິນຄ້າໃນສາງຂອງຜະລິດຕະພັນທີ່ຕ້ອງໃຊ້ໄດ້."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "Bills of Materials"
msgstr "ລາຍການວັດສະດຸ (BOM)"

#. module: construction
#: model:product.template,name:construction.product_product_5_product_template
msgid "Building Blocks 39x14x19cm"
msgstr "ດິນຈີ່ບັອກ 39x14x19ຊມ"

#. module: construction
#: model:project.task.type,name:construction.planning_project_stage_4
msgid "Cancelled"
msgstr "ຍົກເລີກແລ້ວ"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "Centralize all the important information 📝"
msgstr "ລວມສູນຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ສຳຄັນທັງໝົດ 📝"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "Construction"
msgstr "ການກໍ່ສ້າງ"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Create an opportunity each time you face a potential customer, receive a "
"phone call, etc."
msgstr ""
"ສ້າງໂອກາດການຂາຍທຸກຄັ້ງທີ່ທ່ານພົບລູກຄ້າທີ່ມີທ່າແຮງ, ໄດ້ຮັບສາຍໂທລະສັບ ແລະ ອື່ນໆ."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "Dashboard ➡️ Your project's status at a glance."
msgstr "ແຜງຄວບຄຸມ ➡️ ສະຖານະຂອງໂຄງການຂອງທ່ານໃນທັນທີ."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "Do you want to go further?"
msgstr "ທ່ານຕ້ອງການໄປຕໍ່ບໍ່?"

#. module: construction
#: model:project.task.type,name:construction.planning_project_stage_3
msgid "Done"
msgstr "ສຳເລັດແລ້ວ"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "Down Payment"
msgstr "ເງິນມັດຈຳ/ເງິນຈ່າຍລ່ວງໜ້າ"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"During and after the construction project, provide a five star customer service by answering the questions from your customer through the\n"
"            <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Helpdesk</font></strong> app. All the emails sent to"
msgstr ""
"ໃນລະຫວ່າງ ແລະ ຫຼັງໂຄງການກໍ່ສ້າງ, ໃຫ້ບໍລິການລູກຄ້າລະດັບຫ້າດາວໂດຍການຕອບຄຳຖາມຈາກລູກຄ້າຂອງທ່ານຜ່ານ"
"ແອັບ\n"
"            <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Helpdesk</font></strong>. "
"ອີເມລທັງໝົດທີ່ສົ່ງໄປຫາ"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "Easily create beautiful quotations 💲"
msgstr "ສ້າງໃບສະເໜີລາຄາທີ່ສວຍງາມໄດ້ງ່າຍໆ 💲"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "Efficiently schedule the work 📆"
msgstr "ວາງແຜນວຽກງານຢ່າງມີປະສິດທິພາບ 📆"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "Enrich the core apps by installing the following ones."
msgstr "ເພີ່ມປະສິດທິພາບແອັບຫຼັກໂດຍການຕິດຕັ້ງແອັບຕໍ່ໄປນີ້."

#. module: construction
#: model:account.analytic.account,name:construction.account_analytic_account_2
msgid "Field Service"
msgstr "ການບໍລິການພາກສະໜາມ"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"For each ordered material, don't forget to fill the analytic distribution in"
" which you will be able to set for which project it will be used."
msgstr ""
"ສຳລັບແຕ່ລະວັດສະດຸທີ່ສັ່ງຊື້, ຢ່າລືມຕື່ມຂໍ້ມູນການແຈກຢາຍການວິເຄາະ ເຊິ່ງທ່ານຈະສາມາດກຳນົດໄດ້ວ່າຈະໃຊ້ສຳລັບໂຄ"
"ງການໃດ."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"From WH ➡️ Deliveries from your warehouse to this specific construction site"
msgstr "ຈາກສາງ ➡️ ການຈັດສົ່ງຈາກສາງຂອງທ່ານໄປຫາສະຖານທີ່ກໍ່ສ້າງນີ້ໂດຍສະເພາະ"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If a technical operation such as a repair is needed, directly create a task in the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Field Service</font></strong> project from a ticket. Then assign it and schedule it to quickly solve the\n"
"            problem. Your employee will be able to use some material to fix the issue. Then these materials and the time spent could be invoiced to the customer."
msgstr ""
"ຫາກຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງມີການປະຕິບັດງານທາງເຕັກນິກ ເຊັ່ນ ການສ້ອມແປງ, ໃຫ້ສ້າງໜ້າວຽກໃນໂຄງການ <strong>"
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ການບໍລິການພາກສະໜາມ</font></strong> ຈາກໃບແຈ້ງບັນຫາໂ"
"ດຍກົງ. ຈາກນັ້ນມອບໝາຍ ແລະ ວາງແຜນເພື່ອແກ້ໄຂ\n"
"            ບັນຫາຢ່າງວ່ອງໄວ. ພະນັກງານຂອງທ່ານຈະສາມາດໃຊ້ວັດສະດຸບາງຢ່າງເພື່ອແກ້ໄຂບັນຫາ. ຈາກນັ້ນ"
"ວັດສະດຸເຫຼົ່ານີ້ ແລະ ເວລາທີ່ໃຊ້ໄປສາມາດອອກໃບເກັບເງິນໃຫ້ລູກຄ້າໄດ້."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If the customer replies to the email, the answer is automatically logged in the chatter on the right of the screen. Thereby, all the discussions regarding the quotation, its updates, and its fine tuning are attached, and the history\n"
"            can be easily consulted by all the involved users"
msgstr ""
"ຖ້າຫາກລູກຄ້າຕອບກັບອີເມລ, ຄຳຕອບຈະຖືກບັນທຶກລົງໃນສ່ວນສົນທະນາ (Chatter) ຢູ່ເບື້ອງຂວາຂອງໜ້າຈໍໂດຍອັດຕ"
"ະໂນມັດ. ດ້ວຍເຫດນັ້ນ, ທຸກການສົນທະນາກ່ຽວກັບໃບສະເໜີລາຄາ, ການປັບປຸງ ແລະ ການປັບແຕ່ງລະອຽດຈະຖືກຄັດຕິ"
"ດໄວ້, ແລະ ຜູ້ໃຊ້ທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງທັງໝົດສາມາດກວດເບິ່ງປະຫວັດຄືນໄດ້ຢ່າງງ່າຍດາຍ"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If the stock levels are too low, resupply the materials from the\n"
"            <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Purchase</font></strong> app by creating a purchase order linked to the right vendor. In the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Contact</font></strong> app, you can easily manage all your\n"
"            preferred vendors and don't hesitate to set a warning to remind if there is a minimum amount to get free transport costs."
msgstr ""
"ຫາກລະດັບສິນຄ້າໃນສາງຕ່ຳເກີນໄປ, ໃຫ້ຕື່ມວັດສະດຸຈາກແອັບ\n"
"            <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ການຈັດຊື້</font></strong> ໂດຍ"
"ການສ້າງໃບສັ່ງຊື້ທີ່ເຊື່ອມໂຍງກັບຜູ້ສະໜອງທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ. ໃນແອັບ <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-"
"1\">ຜູ້ຕິດຕໍ່</font></strong>, ທ່ານສາມາດຈັດການ\n"
"            ຜູ້ສະໜອງທີ່ທ່ານພໍໃຈໄດ້ຢ່າງງ່າຍດາຍ ແລະ ຢ່າລືມຕັ້ງຄຳເຕືອນເພື່ອເຕືອນຫາກມີຍອດສັ່ງຊື້ຂັ້ນຕ່ຳເພື່ອ"
"ໃຫ້ໄດ້ຄ່າຂົນສົ່ງຟຣີ."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you want to push your quotation building much further and add all the "
"power of Spreadsheet beneath any line of your Sales Orders, use the quote "
"calculation feature."
msgstr ""
"ຫາກທ່ານຕ້ອງການຍົກລະດັບການສ້າງໃບສະເໜີລາຄາຂອງທ່ານ ແລະ ເພີ່ມປະສິດທິພາບຂອງ Spreadsheet ລົງໃນແ"
"ຕ່ລະລາຍການຂອງໃບສັ່ງຂາຍ, ໃຫ້ໃຊ້ຄຸນສົມບັດການຄຳນວນໃບສະເໜີລາຄາ."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If your country benefits from a tax rebate under certain conditions, you can"
" easily apply it to your entire quotation by creating a fiscal position that"
" will automatically replace the default tax rate by the reduced one"
msgstr ""
"ຫາກປະເທດຂອງທ່ານມີນະໂຍບາຍຫຼຸດຜ່ອນພາສີພາຍໃຕ້ເງື່ອນໄຂໃດໜຶ່ງ, ທ່ານສາມາດນຳໃຊ້ມັນກັບໃບສະເໜີລາຄາທັງໝົດ"
"ຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ງ່າຍໆ ໂດຍການສ້າງຖານະທາງການເງິນ (Fiscal Position) ເຊິ່ງຈະປ່ຽນອັດຕາພາສີເລີ່ມຕົ້ນເປັນ"
"ອັດຕາທີ່ຫຼຸດລົງໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ"

